WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:04.099
Hey, good morning family. I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:04.100 --> 00:00:11.450
First off, I want to say thank you for all the likes, all the shares, and all the kind comments down below.

00:00:11.451 --> 00:00:19.379
You all have been a real blessing to us. If you could right now, please subscribe to our channel and click that notification bell.

00:00:19.380 --> 00:00:24.191
It really helps us with the algorithm, and we really appreciate all your support.

00:00:24.192 --> 00:00:30.638
We just want to say thank you and God bless you all so much. Now, I have a word for you today from what the Lord has showed me.

00:00:30.639 --> 00:00:40.050
This was several days ago. Right after I had the Sid Roth interview, I was praying that night and the Lord gave me an open-eyed vision.

00:00:40.051 --> 00:00:49.590
This vision lasted longer than any vision that I've ever had, and each scene lasted for what seemed like a long time for my flesh.

00:00:49.591 --> 00:00:58.778
So I'm going to tell you what I saw at this time. I was caught up; I was interceding, like I always do at night.

00:00:58.779 --> 00:01:04.755
I was interceding for America, for Israel, and for the war and all that was going on.

00:01:04.756 --> 00:01:09.293
But I knew in my spirit there's something going on with our economy.

00:01:09.294 --> 00:01:17.480
The Lord was warning me about another financial crash coming, and so I was just praying over this.

00:01:17.481 --> 00:01:23.845
It was very intense intercessory prayer, praying for the economy and the collapse of the dollar.

00:01:23.846 --> 00:01:31.541
All of a sudden, I'm caught up in the Spirit, and I see in a vision New York City.

00:01:31.543 --> 00:01:40.359
The Lord shows me New York City, and I see Times Square. But I'm noticing when I'm in the vision that there's no people around.

00:01:40.360 --> 00:01:44.553
It's complete; all the lights are on, everything is really bright.

00:01:44.554 --> 00:01:53.272
I can see the marquee signs everywhere, but I'm noticing a couple of snowflakes falling down in Times Square.

00:01:53.273 --> 00:02:05.413
It wasn't a heavy snow; it was just a little bit of snow. I looked around me, and there were no people around; there were just a couple of people—not a lot of people.

00:02:05.414 --> 00:02:14.551
So I was expecting—I don't know if this was late at night or if this was just a time that there were no people out for some reason.

00:02:14.552 --> 00:02:24.847
All of a sudden, I could see from the east a gypsy cart. There were no horses pulling this cart.

00:02:24.848 --> 00:02:41.389
It had vibrant colors on it—it was red, but there were these tassels coming down in the doorframe of this cart, like a tapestry dangling down. The cart was out of control.

00:02:41.390 --> 00:02:58.933
It was moving at a very rapid pace, coming down the main street of Times Square, and it was rocking back and forth as it was out of control, kind of like an old horse buggy carriage whenever it's out of control.

00:02:58.934 --> 00:03:09.649
I could see the wheels touching and going back and forth as it was moving closer to me as I was standing in Times Square in this vision.

00:03:09.650 --> 00:03:16.859
Everything inside of that gypsy cart was falling. I could see the stuff on the shelves, and I could see the light.

00:03:16.860 --> 00:03:36.530
There were those old wick candle lights—those old glass lights that were attached like that, those oil lanterns—and it was moving and swaying back and forth inside of this gypsy cart.

00:03:36.531 --> 00:03:44.112
It ended like that with this part of the vision. Then all of a sudden, I was taken to Miami.

00:03:44.113 --> 00:03:55.855
I was standing in Miami with all these big neon lights again, and I see all these lights, but I'm noticing again there's no people moving around.

00:03:55.856 --> 00:04:07.832
All of these visions of this time are all on the East Coast. Oh, and I forgot to tell you this: I see at this time I'm in Times Square again.

00:04:07.833 --> 00:04:16.072
I'm sorry to jump around. I see a massive moon in the sky. I look up, and my attention is drawn to this massive moon.

00:04:16.073 --> 00:04:24.100
I see a little sliver of it, so I know it wasn't a full moon; it was still just coming up over the horizon. Now I'm going to go back to Miami.

00:04:24.101 --> 00:04:36.919
I see the same moon over Miami, but I'm down here in Miami and I see it, and it's up here now instead of right in front of me in New York.

00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:51.863
It's in a different position because I'm in a different place in the United States, probably 1,500 miles away.

00:04:51.864 --> 00:05:00.945
I'm seeing the same moon is what I'm trying to tell you all. All of a sudden, like I said, I'm noticing there's no people walking around.

00:05:00.946 --> 00:05:08.667
It's completely quiet. It's night, and nightlife is booming in both cities, so everything is just at a standstill.

00:05:08.668 --> 00:05:14.719
All of a sudden, I'm taken up and I'm looking out over the United States.

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:21.494
Then the Lord shoots me up in the sky, and I'm in the throne room.

00:05:21.495 --> 00:05:30.348
All of a sudden, the Lord speaks to me in the throne room and He said, 'Brandon, I told you it's time to come up higher. It's time to come up higher with the fire.

00:05:30.349 --> 00:05:48.882
It's time to come up in a higher place with Me prophetically and what I'm trying to show you for these last days.'He warned me, and so all of a sudden, I could see out over the edge of Heaven, and I could see all these lightning bolts and all this turmoil going down over the Earth.

00:05:48.882 --> 00:05:58.759
I was watching and I was trying to look down, and He told me, 'You cannot prophesy from a place of carnality right where this is on the Earth.

00:05:58.760 --> 00:06:11.960
When you're looking into the situation and you're on the Earth, you need to come up higher prophetically.'So I was trying to prophesy, but being at the throne room of God, I could see Jesus.

00:06:11.961 --> 00:06:24.642
He had a golden scepter in His hand, and on His head He had a crown, and it was purple and gold with jewels all over; it was beautiful.

00:06:24.643 --> 00:06:32.553
He had some kind of fur on the band of this crown, and I could see a cloak around Him.

00:06:32.554 --> 00:06:39.162
He was just sitting there ruling and reigning with the Father, and He told me, 'Sit before Me.

00:06:39.163 --> 00:06:51.706
Sit; be at peace.'There was a place of peace, but whenever you are seeing over in the spirit realm and all this is happening, it's happening so fast.

00:06:51.707 --> 00:06:58.557
I don't know how long He made me sit there, but He wanted me to be at peace and be still.

00:06:58.558 --> 00:07:08.921
Stop with all the drama that you're feeling, because I could feel like a whirlwind inside of all that was going on on the Earth, but He wanted me to just sit there and be still.

00:07:08.922 --> 00:07:23.521
After a moment of yielding—He wanted me to yield. This is what was really happening in the natural for me in this moment because I was so caught up with everything that I was feeling about the economy and what was going on.

00:07:23.522 --> 00:07:30.739
I felt such a troubling, and He told me, 'Just be still. Be still before Me.

00:07:30.740 --> 00:07:40.324
Do not with all this drama, with what you're feeling inside,'because He wanted me to come up higher with what I was about to see.

00:07:40.325 --> 00:08:05.249
So after you rest and you yield, you raise your hands before Him—that's what it was like in this moment—and I said, 'Father, I just yield to You.'Instead of being like a toddler squirming whenever you're holding them and they want to go about their business, it was like saying, 'I'm broken; I just yield to You.

00:08:05.250 --> 00:08:21.405
I'm not going to sit there and squirm in Your lap anymore. I'm going to take that time and just worship You.'I was caught up, and there was so much peace around me at this time, but I had such an urgency to want to pray for what was going on with what I felt.

00:08:21.406 --> 00:08:34.634
He said, 'Come up higher. Come up higher.'So I got quiet before Him, and whenever I got that quiet and I yielded, all of a sudden, I was taken—boom—and I heard this, and I was able to see.

00:08:34.635 --> 00:08:42.491
I was taken back down. I was in the spirit realm, but I was in a place where I was looking out over the United States as a whole.

00:08:42.492 --> 00:08:47.382
He said, 'Oh, I have blessed you. I have blessed you, O America!

00:08:47.383 --> 00:08:58.252
I have blessed you above all nations. I have put you ahead of all nations. You have been called by Me, and I have chosen you.

00:08:58.253 --> 00:09:41.436
I have put a prosperity on you, but I have weighed you in the balance and you are lacking.'He kept saying this to me three times: 'I have weighed you in the balance and you are lacking.'He was quoting Daniel—I'll put it in the description below—'I have weighed you in the balance and I have found you lacking.'All of a sudden, I'm seeing over America a woman.

00:09:41.437 --> 00:09:54.206
She had blonde hair with extensions, fillers in her face, her lips were done up, and her face had Botox in it.

00:09:54.207 --> 00:10:05.414
She had massive breasts from having augmentation on her body, a tiny waist, and she had very tight-fitting, revealing clothes on.

00:10:05.415 --> 00:10:12.746
The Lord was showing me this woman, and He said, 'She is full of pride. You are full of pride.

00:10:12.747 --> 00:10:20.912
You are full of yourself.'It was arrogance before Him, and He was calling out the behavior of the woman.

00:10:20.913 --> 00:10:44.185
I don't know if the woman represented America like a harlot, but He was calling out her behavior and He said, 'I've weighed you in the balance and you've come up lacking.'He was speaking to this woman, but it represented America—full of pride, full of arrogance.

00:10:44.186 --> 00:10:57.483
He said, 'Oh, I have blessed you, and I have made you greater than any other nations.'Then all of a sudden, the pride that He was disgusted with was the way the woman was carrying herself.

00:10:57.484 --> 00:11:17.817
I saw her face and she was so arrogant, looking in a mirror. She was vain, looking at herself, thinking she was all that.

00:11:17.817 --> 00:11:26.062
She was so proud of the way she looked, but she was so fixated on herself that she wasn't looking at what was going on around her.

00:11:26.063 --> 00:11:41.516
All of a sudden, the Lord said, 'I want to show you something.'I saw a massive gold square that was really thick, and it was a supernatural covering that was over Yellowstone National Park.

00:11:41.517 --> 00:11:50.599
He had put a covering over this area, and it was a massive square that went all the way up over those states.

00:11:50.600 --> 00:11:59.173
It was a golden square, and He had sewn it all on those states.

00:11:59.174 --> 00:12:08.817
I could see a golden thread that was weaved all throughout this golden garment that looked very thick.

00:12:08.818 --> 00:12:24.629
