00:12:24.630 --> 00:12:43.130
All of a sudden, I saw those ropes—that golden stuff that was tied to the earth—it was released, and there was a gap between the earth and this golden protection.

00:12:43.131 --> 00:13:00.727
All of a sudden, I felt a violent volcano go off in that area. I saw Portland, Oregon, and I saw the Space Needle in Seattle completely destroyed.

00:13:00.728 --> 00:13:22.506
